# Balencia Design System — Source of Truth

You are building **Balencia**, a premium AI life coaching platform. Dark mode first. Warm, grounded, never corporate. Every UI element must follow these rules. This supersedes ALL previous color/font guidance in any other skill or role file.

## Design Register

Detect automatically from the page's route group and layout:

- **Brand Mode** (landing, marketing, public pages — no dashboard sidebar): Large hero type via `clamp()`, generous whitespace (64-96px between sections), ambient gradient blobs, continuous stroke line motif, full gradient heroes.
- **Product Mode** (dashboard, authenticated pages with sidebar layout): Compact type (16-20px headings max), dense information display, cards as primary containers, restrained palette.

## Color Tokens (60/30/10 Rule)

| Role | Color | Hex | Usage |
|------|-------|-----|-------|
| **Primary (60%)** | Burnt Orange | `#FF5E00` | CTAs, buttons, hero accents, user voice, streaks, progress bars, active nav |
| **Secondary (30%)** | Forest Green | `#34A853` | Growth, success, completion, recovery, milestones, positive deltas, health metrics |
| **Accent (10%)** | Royal Purple | `#7F24FF` | Coach/AI voice, premium moments, projected data, sparkle accents ONLY |

**Neutrals:**

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `ink-900` | `#0A0A0F` | Primary dark background |
| `ink-warm-900` | `#0C0603` | Warm dark variant |
| `ink-brown-900` | `#140A05` | Brown-warm dark |
| `ink-brown-800` | `#211008` | Elevated dark surface, card bg |
| `ink-700` | `#171717` | Secondary dark, card surface |
| `paper-50` | `#FDFDFB` | Lightest paper (light mode) |
| `paper-100` | `#FEFAF3` | Default light background |
| `paper-200` | `#F9F3E6` | Warm surface |
| `paper-300` | `#F2ECD8` | Warm border, card bg (light) |

**Shadows** — Always warm-tinted (brown hue `rgba(33, 16, 8, ...)`), never cold black:
- `--shadow-1`: `0 8px 24px rgba(33, 16, 8, .18)` (subtle)
- `--shadow-2`: `0 18px 48px rgba(33, 16, 8, .22)` (mid)
- `--shadow-3`: `0 32px 80px rgba(33, 16, 8, .28)` (high)
- `--glow-orange`: `0 0 32px rgba(255, 94, 0, .45)`
- `--glow-green`: `0 0 32px rgba(52, 168, 83, .40)`
- `--glow-purple`: `0 0 32px rgba(127, 36, 255, .40)`

**Gradients:**
- `--grad-progress`: `linear-gradient(90deg, #19C9D2 0%, #FFB13D 100%)`
- `--grad-growth`: `linear-gradient(90deg, #FFB33F 0%, #FF5E00 100%)`
- `--grad-status`: `linear-gradient(90deg, #4EDB8C 0%, #FFB33F 100%)`
- `--grad-hero-glow`: `radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 94, 0, .42) 0%, rgba(255, 94, 0, 0) 70%)`

## Typography

**Sora** is the ONLY UI font. All weights: 300-800. `font-family: "Sora", system-ui, sans-serif`.
Chillax is for the logo wordmark ONLY — never in UI, headings, or body.

**Product Mode scale** (dashboard pages):
- Headings: `clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px)`, weight 600-700
- Body: 14px default (range 13-15px)
- Small/meta: 13px
- Buttons/tabs: 14px desktop, 13px mobile

**Brand Mode scale** (landing/marketing):
- Hero h1: `clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.5rem)`, weight 800, letter-spacing `-0.03em`
- Section h2: `clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem)`, weight 700
- Body: 16px, line-height 1.55

Rules: Sentence case everywhere. No Title Case in UI. No exclamation marks. Max line length: 65ch.

## Spacing (8pt Grid)

Valid values: 4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64, 96, 128px. Never 5, 7, 10, 15, 18, 22, 30.

| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--s-1` to `--s-10` | 4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64, 96, 128 |

## Radii

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--r-xs` | 6px | Small details, inline badges |
| `--r-sm` | 10px | Small chips |
| `--r-md` | 14px | Inputs, small cards |
| `--r-lg` | 20px | Buttons, mid cards |
| `--r-xl` | 28px | Primary cards and panels |
| `--r-2xl` | 40px | Large surfaces, hero cards |
| `--r-pill` | 999px | CTA buttons, chips, segmented controls |

Minimum radius on cards/buttons: `--r-md` (14px).

## Motion

**Never use `linear` easing.** All motion uses:
- `--ease-flow`: `cubic-bezier(.65,.05,.36,1)` — signature curve
- `--ease-out-soft`: `cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1)` — UI default
- `--ease-in-out`: `cubic-bezier(.65,0,.35,1)` — two-way transitions

**Durations:** `--dur-fast` 160ms | `--dur-base` 280ms | `--dur-slow` 520ms | `--dur-flow` 1.2s

Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` in all implementations.

## Component Primitives

- **Buttons**: Pill shape (`--r-pill`). Orange (primary CTA), Green (success/done), Ink-700 (neutral/skip), Ghost (transparent + border).
- **Cards**: `ink-brown-800` bg (dark) or `paper-100` bg (light). `1px` soft border. `--r-xl` to `--r-2xl`. `--shadow-1` default, `--shadow-2` on hover. Padding `--s-5` to `--s-6`.
- **Data viz**: Solid orange line (past/actual data), dashed purple line (AI projection), green dots (milestones). Use brand gradients for chart fills.

## Voice/Copy Rules

Grounded coach tone: warm, curious, playful, quietly confident. Never corporate, aggressive, or preachy.
- Button labels: verb-first, max 3 words ("Start workout", "View details")
- Never use: "Optimize", "Leverage", "Unlock potential", "Crush your goals", "AI-powered"
- Signature prompt: "What's worth your attention today?"

## Anti-Patterns (Hard Blocks)

If any of these appear in generated code, fix immediately:

1. Pure black `#000000` as background — use `ink-900` (#0A0A0F) or ink tones
2. Cold shadows using `rgba(0,0,0,...)` — use warm `rgba(33, 16, 8, ...)`
3. Gradient text on body copy — only display/heading text
4. Purple used as background fill (>10% surface area) — accent only
5. Any font other than Sora in component code
6. Border-radius less than 14px on cards or buttons (badges: 6px min)
7. Hardcoded hex values in JSX — use CSS variables or Tailwind token classes
8. `linear` easing on any UI transition
9. Spacing values not on the 8pt grid
10. Exclamation marks in user-facing strings
11. Title Case in labels, tabs, or buttons
12. Nested cards (card inside a card) — use sections or dividers
13. Missing hover state on any interactive element
